snippet.title: Parcel Corps Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab a helmet and slip into your spandex: it’s time to join the gig economy. Parcel Corps, an extreme sports delivery’em-up from developer Billy Goat Entertainment and publisher Secret Mode, is preparing for delivery in 2024.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2015960
